# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-04-15 14:26

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:13
translate chinese jamie14a_b6dcf387:

    # "As I'm leaving for school, somebody calls my name."
    "当我正要去学校时，有人叫了我的名字。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:14
translate chinese jamie14a_b5d0fc44:

    # "Voice" "Hey, [pcname]!"
    "Voice" "嘿，[pcname]！"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:17
translate chinese jamie14a_42b89db9:

    # "Jamie's dad is waving me down and walking towards me."
    "杰米的爸爸正向我招手，朝我走来。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:18
translate chinese jamie14a_8164aaf1:

    # "Wow, he's looking pretty rough. What the hell does he want?"
    "哇，他看起来挺狼狈的。他到底想干什么？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:19
translate chinese jamie14a_cded88c7:

    # "I almost don't even stop. I don't have anything to say to this guy. I want to just keep going to my car and leave."
    "我差点都没停下脚步。我没什么好跟这家伙说的。我只想径直走到车里离开。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:20
translate chinese jamie14a_aead936c:

    # "But something in his expression and his voice slows me down."
    "但他神情和语气里的某种东西让我放慢了脚步。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:23
translate chinese jamie14a_bea7ca65:

    # jd "Hey, [pcname], can we talk for a minute?"
    jd "嘿，[pcname]，能跟我说几句吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:24
translate chinese jamie14a_810a98a2:

    # pc "What do you want?"
    pc "你想要什么？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:25
translate chinese jamie14a_e6116fb2:

    # jd "I want to... apologize."
    jd "我想……向你道歉。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:26
translate chinese jamie14a_65abe2d1:

    # jd "I messed up."
    jd "是我搞砸了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:29
translate chinese jamie14a_e9e8048e:

    # jd "I don't like you very much. I'm sure you know that."
    jd "我其实不太喜欢你。我想你心里有数。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:30
translate chinese jamie14a_f70317e8:

    # jd "You broke her heart. I saw how much it hurt her."
    jd "你伤透了她的心。我亲眼看到她有多痛苦。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:31
translate chinese jamie14a_62f4e049:

    # jd "She stopped going out with her friends. Stopped trusting people."
    jd "她不再和朋友出去玩了。也不再信任任何人了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:32
translate chinese jamie14a_3e24a9b7:

    # jd "And I hated you for that. For hurting my little girl."
    jd "为此，我恨透了你。恨你伤害了我的小女儿。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:33
translate chinese jamie14a_3ef77f3d:

    # jd "When she accepted you back so easily, I didn't understand, and I felt like I needed to protect her from you."
    jd "当初她那么轻易就原谅了你，我无法理解，觉得必须保护她免受你的伤害。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:36
translate chinese jamie14a_4c6162ef:

    # jd "But now she's been hurt again and this time it wasn't you that did it."
    jd "但现在她又受了伤，而这次不是你造成的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:37
translate chinese jamie14a_154a6154:

    # jd "It was me."
    jd "是我。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:38
translate chinese jamie14a_da05beb6:

    # jd "She really loves you, [pcname]."
    jd "她真的很爱你，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:39
translate chinese jamie14a_b624fa00:

    # jd "And she's going to resent me forever if I stand in the way of that."
    jd "如果我阻碍了这份感情，她会永远怨恨我。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:40
translate chinese jamie14a_ab239c58:

    # pc "So you're saying that I can date Jamie again?"
    pc "所以你的意思是，我可以和杰米重新交往了吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:43
translate chinese jamie14a_7ffe4964:

    # jd "I'm saying that I'm going to step aside and let her do what she wants."
    jd "我的意思是，我会退一步，让她随心所欲。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:44
translate chinese jamie14a_47573d93:

    # jd "And I'm going to do my best to get along with you."
    jd "我也会尽力和你好好相处。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:45
translate chinese jamie14a_07df80d6:

    # jd "And I hope that you'll accept my apology for getting too protective and overbearing."
    jd "希望你能接受我的道歉——我之前确实太过保护她，也太专横了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:46
translate chinese jamie14a_a1317b53:

    # jd "I just can't stand seeing her sad."
    jd "我实在受不了看她难过。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:49
translate chinese jamie14a_359770ca:

    # jd "So, I'd like to have you over for dinner tonight, if you're not busy."
    jd "所以，如果你不忙的话，今晚我想请你来家里吃晚饭。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:50
translate chinese jamie14a_ec06b19e:

    # jd "To show Jamie that I'm okay with you two."
    jd "为了向杰米表明，我支持你们俩。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:51
translate chinese jamie14a_bd436701:

    # jd "And to try to repair this whole situation."
    jd "也为了试着修复这一切。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:52
translate chinese jamie14a_19e76fb9:

    # jd "If that's okay with you?"
    jd "如果你愿意的话？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:53
translate chinese jamie14a_35da6d22:

    # pc "Sure, I think I can do that."
    pc "当然，我觉得可以。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:54
translate chinese jamie14a_aec7f7b0:

    # jd "Will you shake my hand and put all this behind us?"
    jd "你能和我握手，把这一切都抛在脑后吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:57
translate chinese jamie14a_a17b9866:

    # pc "Yeah, I think that's a good idea."
    pc "嗯，我觉得这是个好主意。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:58
translate chinese jamie14a_501230c4:

    # jd "Good. I'm sorry again."
    jd "好。我再次向你道歉。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:59
translate chinese jamie14a_5487b9f8:

    # jd "I can see you're not the same as you were back then."
    jd "我看得出来，你已经不是从前那个你了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:60
translate chinese jamie14a_3e716201:

    # jd "I've seen how much happier Jamie has been since you've come back to Skyhill."
    jd "自从你回到斯凯希尔，我看到杰米变得多么快乐。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:61
translate chinese jamie14a_bb7d1c41:

    # jd "I just want her to be happy."
    jd "我只希望她能幸福。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:62
translate chinese jamie14a_78ca39f6:

    # pc "I'll do my best to keep making her happy. I promise."
    pc "我会尽我所能让她开心。我保证。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:65
translate chinese jamie14a_c390597e:

    # jd "Alright, [pcname]. Well I'll see you later tonight."
    jd "好的，[pcname]。那今晚见。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:66
translate chinese jamie14a_bf178f5a:

    # jd "How do you like your steaks?"
    jd "你喜欢怎么烤牛排？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:67
translate chinese jamie14a_2e9a5edb:

    # pc "Medium rare."
    pc "五分熟。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:68
translate chinese jamie14a_778e6fc8:

    # jd "Good answer. See, I like you better already."
    jd "答得不错。瞧，我已经更喜欢你了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:69
translate chinese jamie14a_4a59320d:

    # pc "Okay, see you later."
    pc "好的，待会儿见。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:72
translate chinese jamie14a_0ced9731:

    # "After Jamie's dad leaves, I get in the car and head to school."
    "杰米的爸爸走后，我上了车，朝学校开去。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:73
translate chinese jamie14a_1503cf89:

    # "Guess I'm going to be having dinner with them tonight."
    "看来今晚我要和他们一起吃晚饭了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:74
translate chinese jamie14a_6b9b4f27:

    # "I hope it's not too awkward!"
    "希望不会太尴尬！"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:76
translate chinese jamie14a_20fd986c:

    # "Later that evening..."
    "当晚稍晚些时候……"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:86
translate chinese jamie14_e1943713:

    # "I go home and get dressed, putting on something a little nicer than my work clothes, before walking over to Jamie's house to have dinner with her and her dad."
    "我回家换了身衣服，穿得比工作服稍微体面一点，然后步行去杰米家，和她及她爸爸共进晚餐。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:89
translate chinese jamie14_00286863:

    # "Before I even knock, Jamie's dad opens the door and greets me."
    "我还没来得及敲门，杰米的爸爸就开门迎了上来。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:90
translate chinese jamie14_05eb9994:

    # jd "Hey, [pcname]. Glad you came."
    jd "嘿，[pcname]。很高兴你来了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:91
translate chinese jamie14_fc7fda3f:

    # jd "I wasn't sure you would. I know this is going to be a little awkward for everybody."
    jd "我还以为你不会来呢。 我知道这对大家来说都会有点尴尬。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:92
translate chinese jamie14_87d64340:

    # pc "I think it'll be okay."
    pc "我觉得应该没问题。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:93
translate chinese jamie14_f9d3ac60:

    # jd "Good. I hope so. Come on in, I just put the steaks on the grill."
    jd "好。我也希望如此。进来吧，我刚把牛排放上烤架。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:96
translate chinese jamie14_baa894d7:

    # pc "Where's Jamie?"
    pc "杰米在哪儿？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:97
translate chinese jamie14_a4f2a7fd:

    # jd "She's still up in her room. She's barely left since I made her break up with you."
    jd "她还在自己房间里。自从我让她和你分手后，她几乎都没出来过。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:98
translate chinese jamie14_f3737b26:

    # jd "I'm going to call her down for dinner when it's ready and let you surprise her."
    jd "等饭做好了，我会叫她下来吃饭，让你给她一个惊喜。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:101
translate chinese jamie14_473a3bfb:

    # jd "I think it'll make her happy to see us getting along."
    jd "我觉得看到我们相处融洽，她会很开心的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:102
translate chinese jamie14_217a60e1:

    # pc "I hope so. I'm looking forward to seeing her."
    pc "我也希望如此。我很期待见到她。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:103
translate chinese jamie14_f8b1bf29:

    # pc "I've been missing her the last week."
    pc "过去这一周我一直很想她。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:104
translate chinese jamie14_b320763c:

    # jd "Yeah. I know she missed you too. I'm sorry again."
    jd "是啊。我知道她也很想你。我再次向你道歉。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:105
translate chinese jamie14_d68d94af:

    # pc "It's alright. I know you were just trying to protect your daughter."
    pc "没关系。我知道你只是想保护你的女儿。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:106
translate chinese jamie14_9810dcb5:

    # pc "I'm glad she has a dad who loves her so much. I know she loves you very much too."
    pc "我很高兴她有个如此爱她的爸爸。我知道她也很爱你。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:109
translate chinese jamie14_dde4aef6:

    # jd "Thanks, [pcname]. That makes me really glad to hear."
    jd "谢谢，[pcname]。听到这话我真的很开心。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:110
translate chinese jamie14_884f0447:

    # jd "I hope she'll forgive me for all of this."
    jd "希望她能原谅我做的一切。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:111
translate chinese jamie14_961e07b1:

    # pc "I know she will."
    pc "我知道她会的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:112
translate chinese jamie14_8a978913:

    # jd "My name is Richard, by the way. Rich to friends. I don't know if I've ever really introduced myself."
    jd "顺便说一下，我叫理查德。朋友都叫我里奇。我不确定之前有没有正式自我介绍过。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:116
translate chinese jamie14_4c30d37e:

    # jd "Of course, I hadn't talked to you since you were a punk kid, playing Donkey Kong and sneaking feels in my daughter's bedroom."
    jd "当然，自从你还是个小混混，整天玩《大金刚》还偷偷溜进我女儿卧室摸来摸去的时候，我就没跟你说过话了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:117
translate chinese jamie14_078bc847:

    # pc "Oh we never did that."
    pc "哦，我们才没干过那种事呢。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:118
translate chinese jamie14_acfa9a92:

    # jd "Sure you didn't! And she was just sleeping over at your house last week because your bed is more comfortable."
    jd "才怪！上周她还睡在你家过夜，就因为你的床更舒服。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:119
translate chinese jamie14_e7874c6c:

    # pc "That's right."
    pc "没错。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:120
translate chinese jamie14_f9b86ca6:

    # "He laughs and I find myself laughing with him. He's not so bad when he doesn't seem to want to kill me."
    "他笑了，我也跟着笑了。当他看起来没想杀了我时，其实还挺不错的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:125
translate chinese jamie14_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_031.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_031.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:126
translate chinese jamie14_3b4e87c7:

    # gnd "Uh...What the heck is going on here?"
    gnd "呃……这到底是怎么回事？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:127
translate chinese jamie14_7574532d:

    # jd "Oh, hey honey. I was about to go upstairs and get you. Dinner's ready."
    jd "哦，嗨，亲爱的。我正要上楼找你呢。饭做好了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:128
translate chinese jamie14_23866c5e:

    # gnd "I am very confused right now. Why is [pcname] here?"
    gnd "我现在很困惑。[pcname]怎么会在这里？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:131
translate chinese jamie14_e2bc8a1e:

    # jd "Because I made a mistake."
    jd "因为我犯了个错。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:132
translate chinese jamie14_0ed25bb5:

    # jd "In trying to protect you from getting your heart broken again..."
    jd "本想保护你，不让你再次心碎……"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:133
translate chinese jamie14_1d42c416:

    # jd "... I ended up breaking it myself."
    jd "……结果却是我亲手伤了你的心。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:134
translate chinese jamie14_b2095d7e:

    # jd "I'm sorry honey."
    jd "对不起，亲爱的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:135
translate chinese jamie14_f3239e98:

    # jd "I'm okay with you dating [pcname]. I'm okay with you doing whatever makes you happy."
    jd "你和[pcname]约会我没意见。只要能让你开心，做什么我都支持。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:136
translate chinese jamie14_bb351aa3:

    # gnd "Really, Daddy?"
    gnd "真的吗，爸爸？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:137
translate chinese jamie14_ca7717c2:

    # jd "Really really."
    jd "真的真的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:140
translate chinese jamie14_4e39c56f:

    # gnd "Thank you, Daddy."
    gnd "谢谢你，爸爸。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:141
translate chinese jamie14_04061eae:

    # jd "I love you, honey. I hope you know that."
    jd "我爱你，亲爱的。希望你知道这一点。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:142
translate chinese jamie14_63418466:

    # gnd "I love you too, Daddy."
    gnd "我也爱你，爸爸。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:143
translate chinese jamie14_0b8d1eb2:

    # jd "I'll take the steaks inside and get the table set. I know you two need to talk."
    jd "我把牛排拿进去，去摆好餐桌。我知道你们俩需要谈谈。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:146
translate chinese jamie14_69e44ecf:

    # "He carries the food inside and shuts the back door as Jamie walks slowly to me."
    "他把食物端进屋，关上后门，这时杰米慢慢走向我。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:148
translate chinese jamie14_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice "voices/jamie_009b.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_009b.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:149
translate chinese jamie14_24b3ee56:

    # gnd "I'm sorry that I cut things off like I did."
    gnd "我很抱歉当时那样突然断了联系。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:150
translate chinese jamie14_4addc5b6:

    # gnd "I didn't know what to do."
    gnd "我当时不知道该怎么办。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:151
translate chinese jamie14_607ff19c:

    # gnd "I've been crying about it all week."
    gnd "这一周我为此哭了好久。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:153
translate chinese jamie14_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice "voices/jamie_032.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_032.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:154
translate chinese jamie14_83f69a35:

    # gnd "Are we okay?"
    gnd "我们还好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:155
translate chinese jamie14_2e8693f0:

    # pc "Yeah, baby. We're okay."
    pc "嗯，宝贝。我们没事。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:156
translate chinese jamie14_d481f95f:

    # pc "Come here."
    pc "过来。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:159
translate chinese jamie14_e043500c:

    # gnd "I missed you so much."
    gnd "我好想你。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:160
translate chinese jamie14_4295bf3d:

    # pc "I missed you too."
    pc "我也想你。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:161
translate chinese jamie14_c2110f18:

    # "We kiss like that for a long time. She clings to me like she never wants to let go."
    "我们就那样亲吻了很久。她紧紧依偎着我，仿佛永远都不想放手。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:164
translate chinese jamie14_d87fd08d:

    # "Then the back door opens and Rich peeks out."
    "这时后门开了，里奇探头出来。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:165
translate chinese jamie14_774c15a1:

    # jd "Oh, um... sorry. Honey, where is the A1?"
    jd "哦，呃……抱歉。亲爱的，A1酱汁在哪儿？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:166
translate chinese jamie14_8d809a41:

    # "Jamie doesn't break off the kiss to answer, her lips never leaving mine."
    "杰米没有中断亲吻来回答，她的双唇始终贴着我的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:167
translate chinese jamie14_50d35669:

    # gnd "Bottom shelf of the refrigerator door."
    gnd "冰箱门底层。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:168
translate chinese jamie14_13f55642:

    # jd "Okay, thanks honey."
    jd "好的，谢谢亲爱的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:169
translate chinese jamie14_d6a09f10:

    # jd "Um... everything's on the table, if you're ready to eat."
    jd "呃……如果你们准备好了，饭都在桌上。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:170
translate chinese jamie14_fc544f46:

    # gnd "Okay, Daddy. We'll be in in just a minute."
    gnd "好的，爸爸。我们马上就来。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:171
translate chinese jamie14_232ae60e:

    # jd "Okay."
    jd "好的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:172
translate chinese jamie14_103466ed:

    # jd "Um... no rush."
    jd "呃……不急。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:173
translate chinese jamie14_f05f4276:

    # "He closes the door and goes back inside."
    "他关上门，走回屋里。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:176
translate chinese jamie14_22af107a:

    # gnd "You're right, you know. I should have just stood up and told him what was going on a long time ago."
    gnd "你说得对。我早该站出来，告诉他发生了什么。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:177
translate chinese jamie14_16efaa2c:

    # pc "It all worked out in the end."
    pc "最后一切都解决了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:178
translate chinese jamie14_01c5d588:

    # gnd "Yeah, but... what if it hadn't."
    gnd "是啊，但……如果没解决呢？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:179
translate chinese jamie14_e8c450c3:

    # gnd "I really need to work on that. Standing up for myself."
    gnd "我真的得改改这点。学会为自己发声。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:180
translate chinese jamie14_0821365b:

    # gnd "And I will."
    gnd "我会改的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:182
translate chinese jamie14_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice "voices/jamie_033.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_033.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:183
translate chinese jamie14_58ddd8ce:

    # gnd "I'm making a promise. If I want something, I'm going to fight for it."
    gnd "我向你保证。如果我想要什么，我会为之奋斗。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:185
translate chinese jamie14_d41d8cd9_4:

    # voice "voices/jamie_034.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_034.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:186
translate chinese jamie14_e5bd6c1c:

    # gnd "I'm not going to let it slip away again, just because I might make somebody upset."
    gnd "我不会再因为怕让别人不开心，就让机会从指缝间溜走了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:187
translate chinese jamie14_24f5981e:

    # pc "I like that. Your happiness is very important."
    pc "我喜欢这种态度。你的幸福很重要。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:190
translate chinese jamie14_1075fe75:

    # gnd "Well, I'm very happy right now."
    gnd "嗯，我现在很开心。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:191
translate chinese jamie14_cee162e3:

    # gnd "Although if I knew you were coming, I would have dressed up a little. Maybe brushed my hair."
    gnd "不过要是早知道你要来，我本该打扮得体一点的。也许该把头发梳好。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:192
translate chinese jamie14_709e8dfa:

    # pc "You're gorgeous. Don't worry about that. I'm just glad to be here with you."
    pc "你美极了。别担心这些。能和你在一起我就很开心。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:193
translate chinese jamie14_dfd62f7e:

    # gnd "You're so amazing."
    gnd "你真是太棒了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:194
translate chinese jamie14_c77df519:

    # gnd "Let's go eat."
    gnd "我们去吃饭吧。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:198
translate chinese jamie14_1720c2ef:

    # "We go inside and sit with her dad and have dinner."
    "我们走进屋里，和她爸爸一起坐下吃晚饭。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:199
translate chinese jamie14_5d82c2b8:

    # "It's not as awkward as I was expecting it to be. Once he gets talking, Rich is pretty funny actually."
    "气氛并没有我想象中那么尴尬。一开口聊起来，里奇其实挺风趣的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:200
translate chinese jamie14_9c723875:

    # "He talks about his work and asks about my school and work."
    "他聊起自己的工作，还问起我的学校和工作。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:201
translate chinese jamie14_bc6f8d22:

    # "He seems genuinely interested in me and over the course of the meal I can feel him warming up to me a bit."
    "他似乎真心对我感兴趣，在整个用餐过程中，我能感觉到他对我稍微敞开心扉了些。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:204
translate chinese jamie14_ea50946f:

    # jd "I was sorry to hear about your dad. Still no word on what happened to him?"
    jd "听说你父亲的事我很难过。还是不知道他到底怎么了？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:205
translate chinese jamie14_7fbf1a0e:

    # pc "No, not yet."
    pc "没有，还没消息。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:206
translate chinese jamie14_487d47b7:

    # jd "It's really strange."
    jd "真的很奇怪。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:207
translate chinese jamie14_ede84000:

    # jd "We used to talk through the fence pretty often, but I hadn't seen him in months before the police got involved."
    jd "以前我们经常隔着篱笆聊天，但在警察介入之前，我已经好几个月没见到他了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:208
translate chinese jamie14_86681f0f:

    # pc "Yeah, he became a bit of a hermit, I guess. Spent all his time in his office in the basement."
    pc "是啊，他好像变得有点像隐士了。整天都待在地下室的办公室里。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:211
translate chinese jamie14_913c87c9:

    # jd "Well, I hope he turns up."
    jd "嗯，希望他能现身。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:212
translate chinese jamie14_1bbf0a93:

    # jd "Hopefully he just took some time off to himself and he'll come home eventually."
    jd "希望他只是暂时独处了一段时间，迟早会回家的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:213
translate chinese jamie14_e82b335f:

    # pc "I hope so."
    pc "我也希望如此。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:214
translate chinese jamie14_4543d9f2:

    # "Sitting here and talking to Jamie's dad just reminds me how much I miss my own father."
    "坐在这里和杰米的爸爸聊天，让我格外想念自己的父亲。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:217
translate chinese jamie14_09aa50f4:

    # "They are pretty similar actually. Hard-working. Funny."
    "其实他们挺像的。勤劳。风趣。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:218
translate chinese jamie14_fdfc1ad7:

    # "Both of them have lost their wife too."
    "而且他们都失去了妻子。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:219
translate chinese jamie14_c5b26d00:

    # "But while Jamie's dad turned to his family after the death and held them closer, my dad had..."
    "但杰米的爸爸在妻子去世后转向了家人，把他们抱得更紧，而我爸爸却……"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:220
translate chinese jamie14_1adb6623:

    # "... well, whatever my dad had done, I'm not really sure."
    "……嗯，不管我爸当时做了什么，我其实也不太清楚。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:223
translate chinese jamie14_398e8474:

    # "After dinner, Jamie and I sit in her backyard together, looking up at the stars."
    "晚饭后，我和杰米一起坐在她家的后院，仰望着星空。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:224
translate chinese jamie14_c08e5558:

    # gnd "That was really nice."
    gnd "那感觉真好。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:225
translate chinese jamie14_66c0b088:

    # pc "Yeah it was."
    pc "是啊，确实很棒。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:226
translate chinese jamie14_73145f9f:

    # gnd "I love that we don't have to hide anymore."
    gnd "我喜欢我们不再需要躲躲藏藏了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:227
translate chinese jamie14_a8284af3:

    # pc "It's not going to ruin the passion?"
    pc "这不会破坏我们的激情吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:230
translate chinese jamie14_64527f8a:

    # gnd "Absolutely not."
    gnd "绝对不会。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:231
translate chinese jamie14_37ba49d4:

    # gnd "I don't think Daddy is gonna want us having sex at the house or anything..."
    gnd "我觉得爸爸应该不希望我们在家里做那种事……"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:232
translate chinese jamie14_86cdae76:

    # gnd "... but I can't wait to spend another night with you."
    gnd "……但我已经等不及要再和你共度一晚了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:233
translate chinese jamie14_04491fb2:

    # pc "Want to come over tonight?"
    pc "今晚要过来吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:236
translate chinese jamie14_5632c3e4:

    # gnd "Soon, but not tonight."
    gnd "很快，但不是今晚。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:237
translate chinese jamie14_33db0ab9:

    # gnd "I think I need to talk to Daddy some alone, you know?"
    gnd "我觉得我需要和爸爸单独谈谈，你知道的？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:238
translate chinese jamie14_9d09aa00:

    # gnd "It seems like we're better, but we still have some things we need to work through."
    gnd "虽然我们关系好像好转了，但还是有些问题需要解决。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:239
translate chinese jamie14_34b44705:

    # pc "I understand."
    pc "我理解。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:242
translate chinese jamie14_8749741d:

    # gnd "But things are going to be good, I know it."
    gnd "但一切都会好起来的，我知道的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:243
translate chinese jamie14_677d7bb7:

    # gnd "Thanks for everything, [pcname]."
    gnd "谢谢你做的一切，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:244
translate chinese jamie14_fe2167ed:

    # gnd "I know it probably wasn't easy to make tonight happen, to patch things up with Daddy."
    gnd "我知道为了促成今晚的聚会，为了和爸爸和好，你肯定不容易。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:245
translate chinese jamie14_56e12139:

    # gnd "So thank you for doing that. For not holding things against him."
    gnd "所以谢谢你这么做。谢谢你没有因此怪罪他。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:248
translate chinese jamie14_d41d8cd9_5:

    # voice "voices/jamie_022.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_022.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:249
translate chinese jamie14_f9831d1e:

    # gnd "I love you, [pcname]."
    gnd "我爱你，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:250
translate chinese jamie14_5e3e613a:

    # pc "I love you too, Jamie."
    pc "我也爱你，杰米。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:251
translate chinese jamie14_53a4b911:

    # "We lie there for a while longer, holding each other and enjoying the cool night air."
    "我们又躺了一会儿，互相拥抱着，享受着凉爽的夜风。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:254
translate chinese jamie14_f4805d30:

    # "Then I tell her and Rich goodbye and go back over to my house, leaving them to work out whatever they need to."
    "然后我跟她和里奇道别，回到了自己家，留他们去处理他们之间需要解决的事情。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:255
translate chinese jamie14_acdbbb7b:

    # "It feels like Jamie and I took a big step in our relationship today."
    "感觉今天我和杰米的关系迈出了一大步。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:256
translate chinese jamie14_9d2f13b4:

    # "Things are getting more serious. I promised her dad that I wouldn't hurt her."
    "关系变得更认真了。我向她爸爸保证过，我不会伤害她。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:257
translate chinese jamie14_ad87ea57:

    # "I hope I can keep that promise."
    "希望我能信守这个承诺。"

